---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="UCSD CS Student"
	pubDate={new Date('July 27 2025')}
>
	<section class="about">
		<h1>Hi, I'm Jae Hyun Cha </h1>
		<p>
		I'm a computer science student at UCSD. I’m mainly interested in backend development,
		system design, and recently, machine learning.
		</p>

		<p>
		I like working on things that are practical and useful. I enjoy building APIs,
		working with databases, and figuring out how to structure code in a way that makes it easy to maintain later.
		</p>

		<p>
		Lately, I’ve been trying to learn more about how machine learning can be applied to real projects,
		especially things like recommendation systems.
		</p>

		<p>
		Outside of coding, I like working with other people and learning from them.
		I try to keep improving by building personal projects or helping out on team projects.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="skills">
		<h2>My Skills</h2>

		<div class="skill">
		<label>Python</label>
		<progress value="90" max="100"></progress>
		</div>
		<div class="skill">
		<label>Java</label>
		<progress value="80" max="100"></progress>
		</div>
		<div class="skill">
		<label>HTML/CSS/JS</label>
		<progress value="85" max="100"></progress>
		</div>
		<div class="skill">
		<label>Machine Learning</label>
		<progress value="70" max="100"></progress>
		</div>
		<div class="skill">
		<label>System Design</label>
		<progress value="60" max="100"></progress>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="contact">
		<h2>Contact Me</h2>
		<form method="POST" action="https://httpbin.org/post">
		<label for="name">Name</label>
		<input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />

		<label for="email">Email</label>
		<input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />

		<label for="message">Message</label>
		<textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>

		<button type="submit">Send</button>
		</form>
	</section>

	<style>
		section {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 2rem auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		}

		h1, h2 {
		text-align: center;
		}

		.skill {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		.skill label {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
		}

		progress {
		width: 100%;
		height: 1rem;
		}

		.contact form {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
		}

		input, textarea {
		padding: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		border: 1px solid #ccc;
		}

		button {
		background-color: #1a1a1e;
		color: white;
		border: none;
		padding: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		border-radius: 4px;
		}

		button:hover {
		background-color: #333;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
